~ start
A group rescued me and now I'm in that group. We're called the Scavengers, mainly due to our strict routines. We have lots of people and lots of resources.
This is my final note, to whoeever finds themselves here, if this place isn't filled with acid. Hah, what a shame if all my notes just got dissolved. I'd rather keep them with me, but I don't think I will.
Have faith, have hope. I've convinced my team to search around the sewer's vicinity (mainly because there's good stuff here) in case someone finds themselves trapped.
I have a feeling our adventure is just beginning.
=> END